description:
The Seventh Day Adventist Church was in its infancy but had already made its way into the publishing and health work. Despite its small membership, it soon warranted an education field too. The power of Christian education to support gospel ministry has been evident across the world ever since - wherever the church is strong, education is also strong. The work of education and Redemption are one".

To find out more information about Adventist Education read our extended articles on our website.
